snippet.title: Yet Another Climbing Game Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3329220/Yet_Another_Climbing_Game/

To quote my inspiration: "Only a person who loves pain will reach the peak, because there is no other way." (A random from the internet).

For the few who reach the top, something curious awaits...
